comments.body:
@rhatdan I could but...I think the best way forward is to get more people involved, not just change ownership.  Unless you had some other reason in mind?

@mtrmac and I are both "stuck" in debugging test-internals to figure out what needs fixing in the environment.  I am completely unfamiliar with both the code-base's tests, and the VM environment, so am of little use other than pulling high-level strings :disappointed: 

@ashley-cui has experience working in MacOS for podman, maybe some of her knowledge could be of use here?

Who else knows the skopeo integration tests well, and could help debug them?
